Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.36,0:19:47.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隼人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.03,0:19:53.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.21,0:19:55.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.27,0:19:57.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,办到了呢 隼人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.86,0:19:59.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的超感动的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.26,0:20:02.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常精采的比赛哦 隼人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.98,0:20:04.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你们大家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.45,0:20:05.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日吉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.20,0:20:29.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你了 隼人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.27,0:20:34.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我曾经只想着要赢你而跑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.31,0:20:37.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为恨你夺走了我的地位
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.35,0:20:41.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过在和你经过了这场精采的战斗后
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.27,0:20:42.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我终于释怀了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.64,0:20:44.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就让我们互相勉励吧 隼人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.72,0:20:45.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日吉先生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.99,0:20:48.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不是你的话 我也不会有今天
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.19,0:20:50.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常谢谢你
